item.title: CVE-2022-22770|2024-08-03T03:21:49.164Z -- tibco%20software%20inc. -- tibco%20auditsafe
item.description: The Web Server component of TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO AuditSafe contains an easily exploitable vulnerability that allows an unauthenticated attacker with network access to execute API methods on the affected system. Affected releases are TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO AuditSafe: versions 1.1.0 and below.
